window.__KB.push({"t": "申請更換服務保險顧問的指引 (只限個人保險產品) 1. 所需文件  客戶申請書正本 2. 客戶申請書所載資料  保單持有人姓名  保單編號  新服務保險", "f": "AC001.pdf", "s": "申請更換服務保險顧問的指引 (只限個人保險產品) 1. 所需文件  客戶申請書正本 2. 客戶申請書所載資料  保單持有人姓名  保單編號  新服務保險顧問姓名  新服務保險顧問編號  保單持有人簽署  簽署日期 3. 保障規定  該保單現有服務保險顧問 (Current Servicing Insurance Advisor) 將獲給予為期十四 日的保障期。  更換服務保險顧問保障規定通知，將透過宏利全接觸的「保險顧問通訊系統 (Agent Notification System - ANS）」發送至現有服務保險顧問 (Current Servicing Insurance Advisor) 、 新 被 委 任 服 務 保 險 顧 問 (Proposed Servicing Insurance Advisor) 及兩人的分區總監 (DD) 。  更換服務保險顧問的申請會於十四日保障期結束後生效。 4. 申請資料齊備  公司會向客戶發出確認函。  更換服務保險顧問確認通知，亦將透過宏利全接觸的「保險顧問通訊系統 (Agent Notification System - ANS ） 」 發 送 至 現 有 服 務 保 險 顧 問 (Current Servicing Insurance Advisor) 、 新委任服務保險顧問 (New Assigned Servicing Insurance Advisor) 及兩人的直屬經理。 5. 申請資料不全  新被委任服務保險顧問會收到申請被拒通知，以與客戶作出相關跟進。 6. 遞交  請將完整的申請書遞交至經銷報酬部(MT 22/F) 。 Confidential To: Manulife (International) Limited This is a fillable form. Please fill it in and print it for signature. 此表格是可輸入的。請輸入及打印以供簽署。 For Indiviual Financial Products Only 只限個人保險產品 Print Reset Save Request for Change of Servicing Insurance Advisor Form 申請更換服務保險顧問表格 Name of Policy Owner 保單持有人姓名 (As shown on Identity Document 如身份證明文件所示) Surname 姓 Given Name 名 Policy No(s) 保單編號 (For Individual Financial Products Only 只限個人保險產品) 1st Policy No 第一份保單編號: - - (For 10 Digits only / 只限 10 位數字) 2nd Policy No (if any) 第二份保單編號 (如有): - - (For 10 Digits only / 只限 10 位數字) 3rd Policy No (if any) 第三份保單編號 (如有): - - (For 10 Digits only / 只限 10 位數字) 4th Policy No (if any) 第四份保單編號 (如有): - - (For 10 Digits only / 只限 10 位數字) 5th Policy No (if any) 第五份保單編號 (如有): - - (For 10 Digits only / 只限 10 位數字) Remark: If more than 5 policies, please use additional form(s). 注意: 如保單數量超逾 5 份，請另加填表格。 On the above policy(ies), I would like to request for the change of servicing insurance advisor to the following person. 本人欲申請將上述保單的服務保險顧問更改為以下保險顧問。 Insurance Advisor's Name 保險顧問姓名: _________________________________________________________________ Insurance Advisor's Code 保險顧問編號: _____________________________________ Signature of Policy Owner 保單持有人簽名 _____________________________________ Date (DD/MM/YYYY) 日期 (日/月/年)"});
window.__KB.push({"t": "Loss/Replacement Form for Agent Card/Access Card Please return this form to MT 2", "f": "AS05.pdf", "s": "Loss/Replacement Form for Agent Card/Access Card Please return this form to MT 22/F Agency Support Dept. Agent Card (HK$50 replacement fee) Access Card (HK$100 replacement fee) Lift Label (HK$40 replacement fee) – only applicable for agents located at Manulife Place Agent Name:__________________________ Agent Code:________________________ District Code:__________________________ Office Location:_____________________ Contact No.:___________________________ Reason of Replacement Request: ____________________________________________________________________________ ____________________________________________________________________________ Request Date:________________________ Agent Signature:______________________ Authorization of District Director (DD or above) District Director District Director Name:______________________________ Signature:____________________________ Note: ⚫ Please make a cross cheque payable to “Manulife” and submit together with your application form to MT 22/F Agency Support. ⚫ For Agent Card, please attach a photo (passport size) and write your name and agent code at the back of your photo. ⚫ For inquiry, please email to \"Agency_Support_HK@manulife.com\". For Agency Support Department Use Only. Card Reissued Date:_____________________ Handled by:____________________________ Received by Agent:______________________ Receive Date:__________________________ INTERNAL Form AS05(02/2023)"});
window.__KB.push({"t": "Guide to Filling in the “Claim Form For Payment Of MPF Accrued Benefits (“Benefi", "f": "BEN-WR_Guide.pdf", "s": "Guide to Filling in the “Claim Form For Payment Of MPF Accrued Benefits (“Benefits”) On Grounds Of Attaining The Retirement Age Of 65 Or Early Retirement” (“the Form”) Please have the following documents/information ready before filling in the Form: 1. Your/ scheme member’s HKID card copy. / 2. The original statutory declaration form on early retirement (Form-MPF(S)---W(SD1)) [Applicable to Early Retirement Claim Only]. MPF(S)–W(SD1) [ ] 3. Determined withdrawal account(s) and option⬧. ⬧ ⬧ You may withdraw the benefits • either from all accounts or selected account(s) under Manulife Global Select (MPF) Scheme (“the Scheme”), and • either in a lump sum, a specified amount or monthly withdrawal per standing instruction (for Manulife MPF Interest Fund ONLY). 1. Section I - Details Of The Scheme Member / Claimant – Fill in your information as required in this part. 2. Section II – Details Of The Claim – Please tick the appropriate box to indicate the ground of your claim. If you are the scheme member, simply skip this part. BEN-WR Guide (Sep 2024) If you have previously withdrawn the benefits from the same account(s) by instalments with the same ground as stated, you may simply tick this box and do not need to provide the required documents again.  I have previously withdrawn the benefits by instalments on the below grounds from all the accounts specified in Section II(2), therefore, I DO NOT provide the required documents for this claim again. 本人之前曾基於下述理由從第 II(2)部份指明的所有帳戶分 期提M取an權uli益fe ，(In因ter此na毋tio須na就l) L是im次ite申d 索再次提供所需文件。 2. Section II – Details Of The Claim – “ALL” or “Selected” account(s)? Please specify. Scheme member account number can be found on documents/ statements sent by Manulife, e.g. the notice of acceptance, the member benefit statement. The amount specified MUST be in a whole number. If “Option 2” selected, the below must be indicated: Select either ONE option, otherwise the request CANNOT be processed. • (a) One off Withdrawal ; or • (b) Standing Instruction for Monthly Withdrawal (Not applicable to employee contribution account) 3. Section III – Authorization & Declaration Authorization & Declaration – Sign here and the signature must be the same as your specimen signature previously submitted to Manulife. BEN-WR Guide (Sep 2024) Manulife (International) Limited"});
