window.__KB.push({"t": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE SYSTEMIC LUPUS ERYTHEMATOSUS Policy No. 保單編號： 重病保障索", "f": "C23.pdf", "s": "CLAIM FORM FOR MAJOR DISEASE SYSTEMIC LUPUS ERYTHEMATOSUS Policy No. 保單編號： 重病保障索償表格 － 紅斑狼瘡 PART II – This Attending Physician’s Statement must be completed by a qualified and registered physician at the insured’s expense 第二部份 – 本應診醫生報告必須由受保人自費聘請之合資格註冊醫生填寫 1. Name of Patient 病人姓名 2. I.D. Card No. 身份證號碼 3. Age 年齡 4. Are you the patient's usual medical attendant? 閣下是否病人之私人醫生？ No 否 Yes 是 If \"Yes\", give details 若「是」，請填寫有關資料。 Period of Consultation Past Health History 應診期間 病人過往健康情況 5. a) Date on which you first attended the patient for this disease (S.L.E.). 首次為病人診治是項病症（紅斑狼瘡）之日期。 b) What was the symptom(s) experienced prior to the first consultation? And for how long? 病人首次求診前有何症狀？該等症狀已存在多久？ c) When was the patient informed of the diagnosis? (Please give exact date) 何時通知病人診斷結果？（請填寫準確日期） 6. Give full and exact details of the diagnosis. 請詳盡填寫確實診斷資料。 7. Had the patient any past history of the disease specified above or related illness? 病人過往曾否患有上述疾病或有關疾病？ No 否 Yes 有 If \"Yes\", give details 若「有」，請填寫有關資料。 Name of Attended Physician(s) Date of Consultation Address(es) Exact Diagnosis 應診醫生姓名 診治日期 地址 確實診斷資料 8. Is there anything in the patient's family history which would have increased the risk of S.L.E.? 病人之家庭背景有否任何增加病人患上紅斑狼瘡機會之事項？ 9. Please give details of the patient's habits in relation to alcohol, drugs and smoking. 請填寫病人飲酒、吸毒或吸煙習慣之詳情。 10. Please describe the underlying cause of S.L.E.. 請指出導致紅斑狼瘡之原因。 11. Is there any kind of internal disorder associated with systemic lupus erythematosus? 紅斑狼瘡是否與任何疾病有關？ 12. Is there any evidence of auto-antibodies directed against various self-antigens? 病人有否產生自體抗體侵襲自體抗原？ 13. Is the S.L.E. involved with kidneys Type III to Type V Lupus nephritis? If renal biopsy is done, please advise the finding(s) and supply a copy of biopsy for reference. 病人的紅斑狼瘡是否涉及第三至第五級狼瘡腎炎？如病人已接受腎活組織檢查，請說明檢驗結果及提供活組織檢查副本以供參考。 14. Is the S.L.E. involved with central nervous system? If yes, please give details of radiological investigations, M.R.I., C T scan, laboratory evidence and any other test results for reference. 病人的紅斑狼瘡是否涉及中樞神經系統？如是，請提供放射檢驗、磁力共振、電腦斷層掃描、實驗室證據或其他檢驗結果的詳情以供參考。 15. Was the diagnosis certified by a specialist in Rheumatology and Immunology? If so, please provide us with the name and address of specialist. 病人是否經風濕病學及免疫學專科醫生診斷患有該疾病？如是，請提供該醫生的姓名及地址。 16. Please give details of radiological investigations, M.R.I., C T scan, laboratory evidence and any other test results for reference. 請提供放射檢驗、磁力共振、電腦斷層掃描、實驗室證據或其他檢驗結果的詳情以供參考。 17. Please provide details of physicians to whom the patient has been referred or attended for this disease. 請提供曾為病人診治是項病症之醫生資料。 (We would be grateful for copies of any relevant medical report that are available ) （敬請提供任何有關醫療報告副本） Name of Physician(s) and/or Hospital(s) Address(es) Date of Consultation(s) and/or Period of Confinement(s) 醫生姓名及／或醫院名稱 地址 診治及／或留院日期 18. If there is any further information which, in your opinion, will assist us in assessing this claim, please furnish such information below. 閣下認為有否其他資料可協助本公司審核是項索償申請？請提供有關資料。 5 Signature 簽署 Date 日期 Qualification 資格 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C23 (11/2025) Name of Physician (with stamp) 醫生姓名（連印章） Address 地址 Tel. No. 電話號碼 1 of 1"});
window.__KB.push({"t": "NOTICE OF POTENTIAL CLAIM FOR LONG TERM CARE CONTINUING INCOME BENEFIT 長期護理持續入息保", "f": "C29.pdf", "s": "NOTICE OF POTENTIAL CLAIM FOR LONG TERM CARE CONTINUING INCOME BENEFIT 長期護理持續入息保障潛在索償通知書 Personal Details of Insured 受保人個人資料 Branch code 分行編號 Advisor code 保險顧問編號 Advisor’s name 保險顧問姓名 Contact no. 聯絡電話 1. Name of Insured 受保人姓名 2. HKID/Passport No. 香港身份證／護照號碼 3. Sex 性別 Location 地點 Surname 姓 Given Name 名 4. Date of Birth 出生日期 5. Contact No. 聯絡電話： Male 男 Female 女 DD 日 MM 月 YYYY 年 6. Residential Address 住宅地址 Residence 住宅 Mobile Phone 流動電話 Other 其他 7. Current Type of Residence 目前的住宅類別 Private House or Apartment 私人樓宇 Care & Attention Home 療養院 Other (please specify) 其他（請註明）： Government Housing 政府屋苑 Nursing Home 護理院 Home for the Aged 老人院 Hospital 醫院 Hostel 宿舍 Attending Physician Information 主診醫生資料 8. Physician Information 醫生資料： Name of Physician 醫生姓名 Address 地址 Contact No. 聯絡電話 Insured’s Health Conditions 受保人健康狀況 9. Please answer “No” or “Yes” to the right of each Activity of Daily Living listed below, to indicate your current ability to perform each Activity: 在下列日常生活活動中，請在右邊填上「否」或「是」，以反映閣下目前進行每項活動的能力： a) Need assistance transferring in and out of a chair or bed 需要行動協助，才可坐上及離開座椅及上落床 b) Need assistance with toileting, getting to and from and off the toilet, maintaining reasonable level of personal hygiene and care for clothing 需要如廁協助，才可往返洗手間；坐上及離開座廁；整理身上衣物，並保持合理程度之個人衛生 c) Need assistance with bathing, washing self either in tub or shower, or by sponge bath 需要沐浴協助，才可浸浴、 淋浴或以海綿自我清洗 d) Need assistance with dressing, including putting on and taking off braces or artificial limbs 需要更衣協助，包括 穿帶以及解開支架或矯正器 e) Need assistance with managing bowel or bladder functions (continence) 需要協助才可控制肛門及膀胱的功能（自制） f) Need assistance with eating food that has been prepared and made available 需要協助才可進食預先準備妥當之食物 The Chinese version of this claim form is for reference only. In the event of conflicts between the Chinese and English versions, the English version shall prevail. 此索償表格之中文譯本只供參考之用，若與英文有異，一概以英文為準。 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C29 (11/2025) 1 of 6 Insured’s Health Conditions (continued) 受保人健康狀況（續） 10. Please provide the following details for each Activity of Daily Living for which “Yes” was checked in Question 9. 如第9題的日常生活活動方面的選項為「是」，請填寫下列資料。 Activity 活動 Date Disability Began 喪失能力的日期 (DD日/MM月/YYYY年) Who Assists? (Family, Paid Helper) How Often? (number of times per day or week) 由誰人協助？（家人、傭人） 次數（每日或每週的次數） a) Transferring 行動 b) Toileting 如廁 c) Bathing 沐浴 d) Dressing 更衣 e) Continence 自制 f) Eating 進食 11. Please indicate a “No” or “Yes” to the right of each question below and explain the answer, if requested. 請在問題的右邊填上「否」或「是」，並應要求附上說明。 a) Do you have any difficulty with your memory? 閣下的記憶力有沒有問題？ If yes, please explain 如「有」，請詳述： b) Is memory trouble or confusion the main reason you need assistance? 閣下需要協助的主要原因是否因記憶問題或記性模糊所致？ c) Do you have any difficulty with your hearing? 閣下有沒有聽覺方面的障礙？ If yes, please explain 如「有」，請詳述： d) Do you have any difficulty with your sight? 閣下有沒有視覺問題？ If yes, please explain 如「有」，請詳述： e) What is your height? 閣下的身高是多少？ How much do you weigh? 閣下的體重是多少？ ft 呎 in 吋/ lbs 磅/ m米 kgs 公斤 Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C29 (11/2025) 2 of 6 Insured’s Health Conditions (continued) 受保人健康狀況（續） 12. a) Please list your current health conditions below, and date each began 請列出閣下目前的健康狀況及病患開始日期： Current Health Conditions/Diagnoses 目前的健康狀況／診斷 Date Began 開始日期 (MM月/YYYY年) b) Please list any past health conditions and/or surgeries that help explain your long term care needs: 請列出閣下過去的健康狀況及／或手術，以解釋閣下為何需長期接受護理： Past Health Conditions and/or Surgeries 過去的健康狀況及／或手術 Date 日期 (MM月/YYYY年) 13. Please list all medications you currently take, along with the dose and how often you take each one: 請列舉閣下現時服用之所有藥物，並註明劑量及每項的服用次數：(Example: Digoxin 0.125mg once a day 如: 錠劑 0.125mg 每天一次) 14. When were you last in either a hospital or nursing facility? 閣下上一次入住醫院或療養院是在何時？ Admission Date 入院日期： Institution Name 機構名稱： Institution Address 機構地址： What was the reason for your admission 入住原因： Discharge Date 出院日期： Manulife (International) Limited 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司 C29 (11/2025) 3 of 6 Declaration and Authorization 聲明及授權 I/We hereby declare that the answers to the above questions are full and true to the best of my/our knowledge. I/We further authorize any physician, hospital, insurance company, claims investigation company, government authority or organization that has any record or knowledge of me/us, my/ our health or my/our activities (including records relating to Social Welfare, Workers’ Compensation, credit, financial, earnings and employment history) to furnish to Manulife (International) Limited (“Manulife”) or its authorized representative such information including without limitation all information with respect to any illness or injury, medical history, consultation, prescription or treatment and copies of all hospital or medical records. A photostatic copy of this authorization shall be as effective and valid as the original. 本人／我們特此聲明填報於本表格內之資料已是本人／我們所知之全部並為真實無訛。本人／我們茲授權任何醫生、醫院、保險公司、賠償調查公司、政府 有關部門或其他持有本人／我們個人資料、健康狀況或記錄（包括有關本人／我們所獲之社會福利及勞工賠償、本人／我們之存款、財政狀況、入息及就業 記錄）之組織可以將該等資料，包括但不限於所有有關本人／我們之疾病或受傷，傷患之病歷、診斷報告、藥方或治療及所有醫院或醫療記錄副本等資料予 宏利人壽保險（國際）有限公司（“宏利”）或其代理人。此授權書之複製本與正本具同等效力。 Personal Information Collection Statement 個人資料收集聲明 I/we acknowledge that the personal data provided in this Form will be used by Manulife for the purposes of processing, adjudicating and investigating claims application(s) and request(s) for credit service, approving and underwriting insurance applications, administering and reinsuring policies, complying with applicable laws and other related purposes and for such purposes, may be transferred to such persons or entities (whether within or outside Hong Kong) as: (a) any person in connection with any claims made by or against or otherwise involving customers in respect of any products and/or services; (b) any agent, contractor or third party service provider who provides administrative, telecommunications, computer, information technology, payment, data processing or storage, marketing, mailing,"});
