window.__KB.push({"t": "Application Supplement ҳ‫͡ڭ‬ሗ‫̋ڝ‬༟ࣘ CONTINUATION OF SUPPLEMENTARY BENEFIT(S) UPO", "f": "Form_856_Rider_Continuation.pdf", "s": "Application Supplement ҳ‫͡ڭ‬ሗ‫̋ڝ‬༟ࣘ CONTINUATION OF SUPPLEMENTARY BENEFIT(S) UPON PLAN TERMINATION BY CLAIM PAYMENT 因賠付致計劃終止後延續附加保障 POLICY NUMBER 保單編號 POLICYOWNER 保單持有人 LIFE INSURED 受保人 BASIC PLAN 基本保障 CONTINUED SUPPLEMENTARY BENEFITS 延續之附加保障 CUSTOMER’S DECLARATION 客戶聲明 I, the Policyowner of the policy, hereby declare that I understand and agree to the following changes to the Policy: 本人 [ 此保單之保單持有人] 謹此聲明本人明白及同意下列對此保單之改動： PARTICULARS 詳情 Notwithstanding any provisions to the contrary in this Policy or the Basic Plan, with eﬀect from the Change Eﬀective Date, this Policy shall be amended as follows:不論本保單或基本計劃內有任何相反條款，本保單將由更改生效日期起作出以下修訂： (1) The Basic Plan shall be terminated with no further liability on the part of the Company and no further beneﬁts shall be payable under the Basic Plan. 基本計劃終止，而本公司於基本計劃下再無任何責任，亦毋須再支付任何賠償。 (2) The Continued Supplementary Beneﬁt(s) shall remain in force, but no reinstatement thereof shall be allowed. 延續之附加保障維持生效，但不可就其申請復效。 (3) All Supplementary Beneﬁts other than the Continued Supplementary Beneﬁt(s) attached to this Policy shall be terminated. 除延續之附加保障以外，本保單所有附加保障全部終止。 (4) Where any of the Continued Supplementary Beneﬁt(s) is expressed by its provision to be terminated when the Basic Plan is terminated, such Continued Supplementary Beneﬁt(s) shall remain in force notwithstanding such contrary provision. However, the Continued Supplementary Beneﬁt(s) shall in no circumstances remain in force beyond the date which otherwise would have been the maturity of the Basic Plan. 即使任何此等延續之附加保障於其條款中訂明會在基本計劃終止時同時終止，該延續之附加保障仍會維持生效，不論有任何具相反意 義之條款 。然而，不論任何情況下，延續之附加保障於基本計劃的原訂到期日以後不再生效。 (5) Where any of the Continued Supplementary Beneﬁt(s) is expressed by its provision to be terminated when the Basic Plan is fully paid up, such Continued Supplementary Beneﬁt(s) shall remain in force notwithstanding such contrary provision. 即使任何此等延續之附加保障於其條款中訂明會在基本計劃繳清時終止，該延續之附加保障仍會維持生效，不論有任何具相反意義之 條款 。 (6) No further supplementary beneﬁts shall be allowed. 不可再附加其他附加保障。 (7) All Inﬂation Protector Option (attached to the Basic Plan and/or the Continued Supplementary Beneﬁt(s), if any) shall be terminated. 所有通脹加保權益（附帶於基本計劃及／或延續之附加保障，如有）全部終止 。 (8) No increase in the Protection Amount or beneﬁt amount of any of the Continued Supplementary Beneﬁt(s) shall be allowed. 不可提高任何延續之附加保障之保障金額或賠償金額 。 (9) No plan upgrade or beneﬁt upgrade under the Continued Supplementary Beneﬁt(s) shall be allowed. 不可提高任何延續之附加保障之計劃級別或保障 。 *OBJTSFORM856* Manulife (International) Limited ҃лɛྪ‫ڭ‬ᎈ਷ყϞࠢʮ̡ Form 856_Rider_Continuation (12/2025) *OBJTSFORM856* Page 1 of 2 Application Supplement ҳ‫͡ڭ‬ሗ‫̋ڝ‬༟ࣘ (10) The General Provisions of this Policy shall be deleted in its entirety and replaced by the Company’s standard provisions including the following 本保單之一般條款將會全部被删除，並由本公司之標準條款（包括以下條款）所取代： PAYMENT OF PREMIUMS 繳付保費 Premiums are payable during the life insured’s lifetime in accordance with the premium schedule on the latest policy change endorsement. Any date in the premium schedule which was based on the assumption that the life insured would be a speciﬁed age on such date will be corrected, if necessary, to agree with the life insured’s true age. 保費支付人須於受保人在世期間，按照最新更改保單資料批註上的保費表繳付保費。如有需要，任何列於「保費表」上，假定受保人 將達某特定年齡之日期，將被修訂至與受保人之真實年齡相符。 Premium due date will be the ﬁrst date of the payment cycle corresponding to the payment mode selected by the Policyowner. Failure to pay a premium on or before its due date to the Company in accordance with the Company’s then payment handling procedures will constitute default in payment of that premium. 保費到期日爲按投保人選擇之繳款方式所訂繳款週期的首日。若未能於每個到期日或之前，按本公司之繳款處理手續繳交保費予本公 司，便作不清償保費論。 A grace period of 31 days from its due date will be allowed for payment of a premium in default, during which time this policy will continue to be in force. If a premium remains unpaid after expiration of the grace period, then, without the necessity of sending or giving to the Owner any notarial or other notice, insurance under the policy will cease to be in force. 保費若於到期日仍未繳清，將有三十一天寬限期，期間保單仍然有效。若保費在寛限期後仍未繳交，則此保單將告失效，而本公司毋 須向保單持有人發出通知書。 Notwithstanding any other provision, premium in default will be deducted from any beneﬁt payable under this policy. 不論有否其他條款，拖欠的保費將從應支付利益中扣除。 SUICIDE 自殺 If the life insured commits suicide, whether sane or insane, before the date 1 year after this policy’s date of issue, the Company’s liability under the policy will be limited to the amount paid to the Company less any amount paid by the Company, the amounts being those paid under this policy. 於本保單簽發日起計一年內，若受保人自殺身亡，不論事發時精神是否健全，本公司之責任只限於將已繳交之保費，在扣除本公司對 本保單之支出後退還。 If the life insured commits suicide, whether sane or insane, before the date 1 year after the date of any reinstatement, the Company’s liability under the policy will be limited to the liability had there been no reinstatement, increased by the amount paid to the Company after reinstatement, excluding the repayment of default premium to the Company, and decreased by any amount paid by the Company, the amounts being those paid under this policy. 以本保單復效日起計一年內，若受保人自殺身亡，不論事發時精神是否健全，本公司之責任只限於保單復效前之責任，如同保單從未 復效，以及退還在保單復效後繳交之保費 ( 不包括不清償保費 ) 扣除本公司對本保單之支出後之餘額。 Please put a “P ” in the appropriate box. 請在適當方格內加上「P」號。 Signed at £ Hong Kong / £ Macau on this 簽署日期： 香港 澳門 Day 日 day of , Month 月 Year 年 ✕ Witness 見證人 (Name 姓名： ✕ Signature of insured 受保人簽署 ) (if aged 18 or above 如 18 歲或以上） ✕ Signature of policyowner 保單持有人簽署 (if other than insured 如非受保人） INSURANCE ADVISOR’S STATEMENT 保險顧問報告 I, the undersigned, hereby declare that I have clearly explained the contents of this declaration to the above-mentioned policyowner. 本人﹝下列簽署人﹞謹此聲明本人已向上述保單持有人清楚解釋本聲明之內容。 ✕ Signature of Insurance Advisor 保險顧問簽署 (Name 姓名： ) Date (DD/MM/YYYY) 日期﹝日 / 月 / 年﹞ Manulife (International) Limited ҃лɛྪ‫ڭ‬ᎈ਷ყϞࠢʮ̡ Form 856_Rider_Continuation (12/2025) Page 2 of 2"});
